.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-COUNT-TOTAL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-count-total \- FEAT-2880 channel-count-total
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-count-total
.SH DESCRIPTION
Total channel count across all peers (FEAT-2880).
.PP
Queries all peer channels via lightning-cli listpeerchannels and returns
the total number of channels regardless of state.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
